'''Google图片搜索'''是[[Google公司|Google公司]]於2001年7月推出的[[图片搜索|图片搜索]]服務<ref>{{Cite news |title = A Quick Way to Search For Images on the Web |author = Zipern, Andrew |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2001/07/12/technology/news-watch-a-quick-way-to-search-for-images-on-the-web.html |work = New York Times |date = 2001-07-12 |accessdate = 2009-09-13 |archive-date = 2020-07-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200717224015/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/07/12/technology/news-watch-a-quick-way-to-search-for-images-on-the-web.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/dajedkncpodkggklbegccjpmnglmnflm?hl=en |title=Chrome插件 |accessdate=2012-07-19 |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017011638/https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/search-by-image-by-google/dajedkncpodkggklbegccjpmnglmnflm?hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[Firefox|Firefox]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/search-by-image-by-google/ |title=Firefox插件 |access-date=2012-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121203214318/https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/search-by-image-by-google/ |archive-date=2012-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>提供擴充功能搜索網絡圖像。

其知名的功能為{{tsl|en|reverse image search|反向图片搜索|以圖片搜尋圖片}}，但因涉入圖片版權爭議，其電腦版介紹頁面已無法使用，改為APP下載使用。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW/search/about/ |title=Google Search About |accessdate=2018-04-25 |archive-date=2019-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216065613/https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW/search/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>目前直接前往Google圖片頁面進行以圖搜圖的動作暫時仍無影響。

==發展及使用者介面==
Google總裁Eric Schmidt表示，Google圖片的建立，是因為他想要看「[[珍妮弗·洛佩兹的绿色范思哲礼服|珍妮弗·洛佩兹的绿色范思哲礼服]]」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.project-syndicate.org/commentary/google-european-commission-and-disruptive-technological-change-by-eric-schmidt-2015-01#yMSC5IlY7sHATDCO.99 |title=The Tinkerer's Apprentice |publisher=ETC |date=2015-01-23 |last=Schmidt |first=Eric |accessdate=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2019-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022072949/https://www.project-syndicate.org/commentary/google-european-commission-and-disruptive-technological-change-by-eric-schmidt-2015-01#yMSC5IlY7sHATDCO.99 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2001年，Google圖片编入了2.5億张图片。2005年，這一數字增長到了十亿。到了2010年，已可搜索100亿张图片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2010/07/ooh-ahh-google-images-presents-nicer.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221125047/https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2010/07/ooh-ahh-google-images-presents-nicer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2010年7月，该服务每天被訪問超过一亿次<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-10693439 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109023819/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-10693439 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年早期，Google圖片更新了使用者介面。當滑鼠游標位於縮略圖上時，便會顯示圖片資訊，如解析度、URL等<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://donutey.com/googleimage.php|title = Updated Google Images UI|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070709113747/http://donutey.com/googleimage.php|archivedate = 2007-07-09|accessdate = 2015-09-04}}</ref>。數周後此功能即被取消。

